<CENTER><FONT SIZE=12>Jeff's Home Page</FONT></CENTER>
<P> Version: 1.8 Last Updated: 09/27/96 <BR>
<P>
This page is perpetually under construction!  So deal!

<P> Thanks to the nice people at <A HREF="http://www.digits.com/">Web
Counter</A>, I'm able to tell you that you're visitor number <IMG
SRC="http://counter.digits.com/wc/-d/4/-rz/jwoodfor@unlgrad1.unl.edu"
ALIGN=middle WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=20 BORDER=0 HSPACE=4> to this page since
03/30/96.  (OK, so it's not all that popular.)
<P> <A HREF="http://world.std.com/~mhuben/libindex.html">Join the struggle against Libertarianism!</A>
<P> Hello!  You have stumbled across Jeff Woodford's home page on the
World Wide Web.  It doesn't have porn or get-rich-quick schemes;
you'll have to go <A HREF=elsewhere.html>elsewhere</A> for those.
Instead this page has personal information about me.  (Yeah, like you
care.)
<P> Many thanks to <A HREF="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~visigoth/">John
Prevost</A>, the sysadmin of this system, for letting me have an
account on his machine.
<P> What you can find on my page:
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="humor/index.html">Jeff's Humor Page</A>
<LI><A HREF="friends.html">Jeff's Friends' Homepages</A>
<LI><A HREF="aphio.html">Jeff's Fraternity Links</A>
<LI><A HREF="chemistry.html">Jeff's Chemistry-Related Links</A>
<LI><A HREF="research.html">Jeff's Research Interests</A>
<LI><A HREF="cv.html">Jeff's Curriculum Vitae (a resume for scientists)</A>
<LI><A HREF="personal.html">Jeff's Educational History</A>
<LI><A HREF="political.html">Jeff's Political Links</A>
<LI><A HREF="other.html">Jeff's Other Links</A>
</UL>
<P> My attempt at writing software: <A HREF="expfit.html">Expfit</A>,
my cool exponential fitting program.  (Really only interesting to
other scientists interested in numerical analysis.)
<P> Comments?  Send them <A HREF="mailto:jeffw@dementia.org">here.</A>
<P> Well that's all for now, I will add more later.  Happy browsing!
</BODY>
