<head>
  <title> Visigothic - Alone - 30 November 1994 </title>
  <base href="http://olivier.dementia.org/~visigoth/">
  <link rel="made" href="visigoth.html">
  <link rel="history" href="visigothic-archives.html">
  <link rel="supercedes" href="visigothic2.html">
</head>

<body>
  <fig align=center src="V.gif">
	<center> <img src="V.gif" alt="V"> </center> </fig>

  <hr>

  <h1> ``Alone'' <br>
        <cite> <font size=4> Edgar Allan Poe </font> </cite> </h1>

  <blockquote>
	From <a href="http://128.180.104.9/jillstuff/welcome.html"> 
		childhood</a>'s hour I have not been <br>
	As <a href="http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/usr/">
		others </a> were; I have not seen <br>
	As <a href="http://www.dementia.org/"> others </a> saw;
		I could not bring <br>
	My <a href="gopher://comtch.iea.com:79//shietala">
		passions </a> from a common spring. <br>
	From the same
		<a href="http://info.cern.ch/hypertext/WWW/TheProject.html">
		source </a> I have not taken <br>
	My sorrow; I could not awaken <br>
	My heart to joy at the same tone; <br>
	And all I loved, I <a href="http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/u/dr4b/home.html">loved</a> alone. <br>
	Then- in my childhood, in the dawn <br>
	Of a most stormy life- was drawn <br>
	From every <a href="http://omega.mac.cc.cmu.edu/">
		depth </a> of good and ill <br>
	The mystery which binds me still: <br>
	From the torrent, or the fountain, <br>
	From the red cliff of the mountain, <br>
	From the sun that round me rolled <br>
	In its autumn tint of gold, <br>
	From the lightning in the sky <br>
	As it passed me flying by, <br>
	From the thunder and the storm, <br>
	And the <a href="http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu/u/ak4q/">
		cloud </a> that took the form <br>
	(When the rest of <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu:8001/afs/cs/usr/mah/www/">
		Heaven </a> was blue) <br>
	Of a demon in my view.
  </blockquote>

  <hr>

  <p>
	Older poems are available in the <a rel="history" href="visigothic-archives.html">
	Visigothic Archives. </a>
  </p>

  <hr>

  <a href="visigoth.html"><img src="vbutton.gif" align=mid alt="[Viz]"></a>
  <a href="music/"><img src="music.gif" align=mid alt="[Music]"></a>

