<head>
  <title> Visigothic - The Sick Rose - 4 June 1994 </title>
  <base href="http://olivier.dementia.org/~visigoth/">
  <link rel="made" href="visigoth.html">
  <link rel="history" href="visigothic-archives.html">
  <link rev="supercedes" href="visigothic2.html">
</head>

<body>
  <fig align=center src="V.gif">
	<center> <img src="V.gif" alt="V"> </center> </fig>

  <hr>

  <h1> ``The Sick Rose'' <br>
	<cite> <font size=4> William Blake </font> </cite> </h1>

  <blockquote>
	<a href="http://cs.indiana.edu/elisp/w3/docs.html"> O </a>
		rose, thou <a href="http://cybercafe.demon.co.uk/ccafe/cres.html">
		art </a> <a href="http://www.lysator.liu.se:7500/etexts/recept/main.html">
		sick</a>: <br>
	The <a href="http://140.142.113.151:8000/linux/linux.html"> invisible
		</a> <a href="http://www.lysator.liu.se:7500/users/neotron/main.html">
		worm</a>. <br>
	That <a href="http://thule.mt.cs.cmu.edu:8001/sf-clearing-house/">
		flies </a> in the
		<a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu:8001/afs/andrew.cmu.edu/usr25/jbde/www/">
		night</a>, <br>
	<a href="wais://gourd.srv.cs.cmu.edu:6000/bovik?"> In </a> the
		<a href="http://www.cm.cf.ac.uk:/Sisters.Of.Mercy/"> howling
		</a> <a href="gopher://freehold.andrew.cmu.edu:79/Xweather">
		wind </a>,
  </blockquote>

  <blockquote>
	Has <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu:8001/afs/andrew/usr24/mh7a/www/"> found </A> out thy
		<a href="news:alt.sex.bondage"> bed </a> <br>
	Of <a href="http://ubu.hahnemann.edu/Misc/Vamp-Mov.html"> crimson </a>
		<a href="http://www.lysator.liu.se:7500/c/"> joy</a>, <br>
	And his <a href="http://www.contrib.andrew.cmu.edu:/usr/ak4q/index.html"> dark </a>
		<a href="http://www.willamette.edu/webdev/principia/"> secret </a>
		<a href="gopher://comtch.iea.com:79/Xshietala"> love </a> <br>
	Does thy <a href="http://gothic.acs.csulb.edu:8080/~vamp/Gothic//index.html"> life </a>
		<a href="http://www.lysator.liu.se:7500/terror/thb_title.html"> destroy</a>.
  </blockquote>

  <hr>

  <p>
	Other poems are available in the <a href="visigothic-archives.html">
	Visigothic Archives. </a>
  </p>

  <hr>

  <address>
	<a href="about.html"> John McClary Prevost </a> -
	<a href="gopher://cmu.edu:79/Xvisigoth+" type="text/plain"> &lt;visigoth@cs.cmu.edu&gt; </a>
  </address>

