<head>
<title> Visigothic Music / bauhaus / The Sanity Assassin </title>
<base href="http://olivier.dementia.org/~visigoth/music/bauhaus/">
<link rel="made" href="../../visigoth.html">
<link rel="up" href="../index.html">
</head>

<body>

<fig align=center src="../../V.gif">
<center> <img src="../../V.gif" alt="V"> </center>
</fig>

<hr>

<h1>bauhaus <br> ``The Sanity Assassin''</h1>

<blockquote>
sinister echos clutching at straws<br>
letter boxes screaming<br>
you try to pin him to the wall<br>
you end up on the ceiling<br>
locked in a dome<br>
the shadows flicker by<br>
he's the madcap pusher<br>
delerium the drug he's dealing<br>
<br>
he drops a capsule in your drink<br>
and spikes your dreams with madness<br>
<br>
he's the sniper in the hills<br>
hiding in the holes in your head<br>
he's the poison in your poison<br>
the razor in your bead<br>
hanging on a picture<br>
eye lid needle and thread<br>
you empty yourself once again<br>
he's always one step ahead<br>
was it whispers in your ear<br>
nothing that you said ?<br>
he's walking your sleep now<br>
he keeps your fat paranoia well fed<br>
<br>
he drops a capsule...<br>
<br>
the sanity assassin stays up all night stalking<br>
the sanity assassin picks off victims like flys<br>
the sanity assassin lets his fingers do the walking<br>
the sanity assassin the crack shot between your eyes<br>
he's got you in his sights<br>
<br>
he drops a capsule...
</blockquote>

