<A HREF="perlcall.html">
the <EM>perlcall</EM> manpage</A>
.
<p><UL><LI>	I32	perl_call_pv _((char* subname, I32 flags));</LI>
</UL>
<p>
<DT><STRONG>

<A NAME="perlguts_perl_call_sv_0">
perl_call_sv</A>

</STRONG>
