<A NAME="perlguts_saferealloc_0">
saferealloc</A>

</STRONG>
<DD>
The XSUB-writer's interface to the C <CODE>realloc</CODE> function.
<p>
<DT><STRONG>

<A NAME="perlguts_savepv_0">
savepv</A>

</STRONG>
