Stack pointer.  This is usually handled by <CODE>xsubpp</CODE>.  See 
<A HREF="perlguts.html#perlguts_dsp_0">dSP</A>
 and

<A HREF="perlguts.html#perlguts_spagain_0">SPAGAIN</A>
.
