<p>
<XMP>
        int strnEQ( char *s1, char *s2 )

</XMP>
<p>
<DT><STRONG>

<A NAME="perlguts_strnne_0">
strnNE</A>

</STRONG>
<DD>
Test two strings to see if they are different.  The <CODE>len</CODE> parameter
