<H1> 
<A NAME="perlembed_name_0">
NAME</A>
</H1>
perlembed - how to embed perl in your C program
<p><p><hr>

<H1> 
<A NAME="perlembed_description_0">
DESCRIPTION</A>
</H1>
<p>
<H2> 
<A NAME="perlembed_preamble_0">
PREAMBLE</A>
</H2>
Do you want to:
<p>
<DL COMPACT>
