<p><p><hr>

<H1> 
<A NAME="perlbook_description_0">
DESCRIPTION</A>
</H1>
You can order Perl books from O'Reilly &amp; Associates, 1-800-998-9938.
Local/overseas is +1 707 829 0515.  If you can locate an O'Reilly order
form, you can also fax to +1 707 829 0104.  <EM>Programming Perl</EM> is a
reference work that covers nearly all of Perl (version 4, alas), while
<EM>Learning Perl</EM> is a tutorial that covers the most frequently used subset
of the language.
<p>
<XMP>
    Programming Perl (the Camel Book):
        ISBN 0-937175-64-1      (English)
        ISBN 4-89052-384-7      (Japanese)
    Learning Perl (the Llama Book):
        ISBN 1-56592-042-2      (English)
        ISBN 4-89502-678-1      (Japanese)
        ISBN 2-84177-005-2      (French)
        ISBN 3-930673-08-8      (German)

