    <h2><i>"Declan B. McCullagh" &lt;declan+@CMU.EDU&gt;</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: German net-legislation due this year
<b>To</b>: Fight Censorship Mailing List &lt;fight-censorship+@andrew.cmu.edu&gt;
<b>From</b>: "Declan B. McCullagh" &lt;declan+@CMU.EDU&gt;
