   involved in from December 1970 to August of 1976 -- about 5 years and
   9 months. From 1973 to 1975 I lived aboard the Flagship Apollo
   ("Flag"), the home of L. Ron Hubbard, the founder of Dianetics and
   Scientology. On Flag, I trained to be an auditor (a Scientology
   counselor).

-Declan


