These can be found at http://www.cic.org

We've added some new listings to our Copyright Resources at
http://www.cic.org/resource.htm, including a link to a new, comprehensive
copyright library at Stanford University.

------------------
Legislative Update
------------------
No recent action in Congress on the NII Copyright Protection Act.


John Raffetto
Creative Incentive Coalition


</pre>

