    <h1>[3403] <a href="dl?thread=Re:+GeoCities+kills+web+site+with+drawings+of+male+nudes&after=3403">Re: GeoCities kills web site with drawings of male nudes</a></h1>
    <h2><i>j.stokes@student.anu.edu.au (Jason Stokes)</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: Re: GeoCities kills web site with drawings of male nudes
