The address you now should use for submitting posts to the fight-censorship
list is:

    fight-censorship@vorlon.mit.edu

This isn't a big change since the old address at CMU has been forwarded to
the above address for months. You should notice no changes in the list --
except some improvements in performance. The old address will be forwarded
to the MIT address for the forseeable future.

If you want to subscribe or unsubscribe, check out the instructions at:

     http://www.eff.org/~declan/fight-censorship/

The above URL will exist until John and I recreate the fight-censorship
archive this weekend. (This means the international section will be back
online, which is now at http://www.eff.org/~declan/global/)

I'd also like to thank Jered for hosting the fight-censorship mailing list
at MIT.

