&gt;But perhaps we can agree that the most vile form of censorship remains that
&gt;done by governments, which buttress their laws with the power of guns,
&gt;tanks, and gallows.

On this point, I'm having a discussion on this topic in news:aus.org.efa..
would anyone care to comment?

From: j.stokes@student.anu.edu.au (Jason Stokes)
