    <h1>[3359] <a href="dl?thread=+ALERT:+Congress+rushing+to+pass+surveillance+plan!++Call+now!+(8/1/96)&after=3359"> ALERT: Congress rushing to pass surveillance plan!  Call now! (8/1/96)</a></h1>
    <h2><i>Voters Telecommunications Watch &lt;shabbir@vtw.org&gt;</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>:  ALERT: Congress rushing to pass surveillance plan!  Call now! (8/1/96)
<b>To</b>: fight-censorship+@andrew.cmu.edu
