    <h1>[3360] <a href="dl?thread=EPIC+Alert+3.14+--+G-7+and+crypto+restrictions+&after=3360">EPIC Alert 3.14 -- G-7 and crypto restrictions </a></h1>
    <h2><i>declan@well.com (Declan McCullagh)</i></h2>
    <pre>
