    <h1>[3362] <a href="dl?thread=Red+Alert,+Call+to+Arms+--+Surveillance+Legislation+in+Congress&after=3362">Red Alert, Call to Arms -- Surveillance Legislation in Congress</a></h1>
    <h2><i>declan@well.com (Declan McCullagh)</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: Red Alert, Call to Arms -- Surveillance Legislation in Congress
<b>To</b>: fight-censorship@vorlon.mit.edu
<b>From</b>: declan@well.com (Declan McCullagh)
<b>Date</b>: Thu, 1 Aug 1996 18:52:21 -0500
