    <h1>[3438] <a href="dl?thread=Re:+UK+Internet+providers+plan+to+restrict+cyberporn&after=3438">Re: UK Internet providers plan to restrict cyberporn</a></h1>
    <h2><i>declan@well.com (Declan McCullagh)</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: Re: UK Internet providers plan to restrict cyberporn
