    <h1>[3439] <a href="dl?thread=Cybergangs+%22in+your+home,+your+living+room,+your+den%22&after=3439">Cybergangs "in your home, your living room, your den"</a></h1>
    <h2><i>declan@well.com (Declan McCullagh)</i></h2>
